onen\")\n| align=\"left\" |\"We'll prepare\"\n|-\n| style=\"background:Azure\" |[[Hindi]]\n|{{N/A}}\n| style=\"background:Azure\" |\"\u0939\u094b \u0924\u0948\u092f\u093e\u0930\" (\"Ho tayyar\")\n| style=\"background:Azure\" |\"Be ready\"\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Hungarian language|Hungarian]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[Tibor Krist\u00f3f|Krist\u00f3f Tibor]]\n| align=\"left\" |\"K\u00e9sz\u00fclj h\u00e1t\"\n| align=\"left\" |\"So prepare\"\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Icelandic language|Icelandic]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[J\u00f3hann Sigur\u00f0arson]] \n| align=\"left\" |\"Vi\u00f0buin \u00f6ll\"\n| align=\"left\" |\"Ready, everyone\"\n|-\n| style=\"background:Azure\" |[[Indonesian language|Indonesian]]\n| style=\"background:Azure\" |Ojay Surawinata\n| style=\"background:Azure\" |\"Bersiaplah\"\n| style=\"background:Azure\" |\"Be prepared\"\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Italian language|Italian]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[Tullio Solenghi]] \n| align=\"left\" |\"Sar\u00f2 re\"\n| align=\"left\" |\"I'll be king\"\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Japanese language|Japanese]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[Haruhiko J\u014d|\u58e4\u6674\u5f66 (J\u014d Haruhiko)]]\n| align=\"left\" |\"\u6e96\u5099\u3057\u3066\u304a\u3051\" (\"Junbi shite oke\")\n| align=\"left\" |\"Be prepared\"\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Korean language|Korean]]\n| align=\"left\" |\uc774\uc131\ud6c8 (Lee Seong-Hun)\n| align=\"left\" |\"\uc900\ube44\ud574\" (\"Junbihae\")\n| align=\"left\" |\"Prepare\"\n|-\n| style=\"background:Azure\" |[[Malaysian language|Malaysian]]\n|{{N/A}}\n| style=\"background:Azure\" |\"Bersedia\"\n| style=\"background:Azure\" |\"Be prepared\"\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Taiwanese Mandarin|Mandarin Chinese]]\n|align=\"left\"|\u4e01\u9054\u660e (D\u012bng D\u00e1m\u00edng) \n|align=\"left\"|\"\u5feb\u51c6\u5907\" (\"Ku\u00e0i zh\u01d4n b\u00e8i\")\n|align=\"left\"|\"Ready to prepare\"\n|-\n| style=\"background:Azure\" |[[Marathi language|Marathi]]\n| style=\"background:Azure\" |[[Mahesh Manjrekar|\u092e\u0939\u0947\u0936 \u09